widgets_values: Please extend the picture outward naturally based on the perspective of the original image, and supplement the details of the surrounding environment on the basis of maintaining the original style. The expanded picture is presented directly in the tone of panoramic description, focusing on the texture, material expression and spatial perspective of the new elements. 宁静的图像向外扩展，揭示了融合到北极般的膨胀的滚动丘陵的无缝延续。这些柔软的起伏的雪沙丘延伸到远处，质地上有微妙的变化，在质地上，光线反射不同，唤起了柔和的沙丘地形。在右边，雪开始形成微弱的线性山脊，暗示了塑造它们的风的定向图案。除此之外，散落的结晶霜散发着场景，捕捉阳光以产生精致的火花。

前景水扩大了镜子状的平静，展示了轻风产生的光滑波纹。浅冰块间歇性地出现在地平线附近，半透明的边缘暗示着较冷的深度上的脆弱层。水闪闪发光，虹彩微弱，反映了上面的蓝色和白色的梯度，几乎无缝地将天空和地形融合在一起。遥远的地平线暗示着微弱的云层开始柔化了场景的鲜明，增强了巨大而未触及的寒冷氛围。这种扩大的全景以纯粹，简约的风格捕捉了冰，雪和水的宁静相互作用。

The cozy chair with soft beige upholstery and a brown curved base sits on a light grey textured carpet, which stretches around the space. Extending outward, the room features smooth cream-colored walls, continuing the warm and neutral aesthetic. On the left, adjacent to the drawer unit visible in the original image, a small, minimalist indoor potted plant sits on a low, modern white table, introducing a natural element for contrast. 

On the right side, a slender floor lamp with a matte black finish and a white fabric shade provides ambient lighting. Beyond this, a tall floor-to-ceiling window, with soft cream curtains partially drawn, allows sunlight to spill into the room, casting soft shadows across the carpet and chair. The backdrop hints at a serene outdoors—lush greenery visible, while the overall architectural feel merges modern minimalism with cozy elegance. Wood grain paneling on the base of the wall and polished metallic accents in smaller decorative elements complete the immersive space.
